@realmoney Consider Lightening Up On Bank Stocks *If you have a short term timeframe I am not selling a share of my bank holdings but for those with a shorter term orientation I would consider taking some profits out of $BAC ($30.21) and $C ($70.40) now based on: * The magnitude

of the move off of the lows. * The brief period in which the move higher has occurred. * The yield on the ten year US note has now rallied by forty basis points in only eight days. I would expect a partial retracement in yields at some point over the near term (which could make

money center banks victims of profit taking). * I maintain a negative market view. That said, I remain very bullish on the financial space over the intermediate term. @tomkeene @jimcramer @SquawkCNBC @cnbcfastmoney @Sarge986 @lizclaman @michaelsantoli @carlquintanilla
